name: Diner Dash: Flo on the Go

description:
Diner Dash: Flo on the Go is an arcade game developed by PlayFirst. It was originally released in 2006. PlayFirst published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Recommended".
Diner Dash: Flo on the Go is available on PC.
